  "title": "Front Desk Receptionist & Administrator",
  "description": "<p>Are you organised, reliable, and naturally warm when interacting with people?<br />We’re looking for a <strong>Front Desk Receptionist & Administrator</strong> to be the welcoming face of our office — and the steady support that keeps our daily operations running seamlessly.<br /></p><p><strong>Key Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Greet and assist guests, clients, and team members with professionalism and warmth</li><li>Manage incoming calls, emails, and general enquiries</li><li>Coordinate schedules, appointments, and calendar updates</li><li>Keep the front desk area tidy, organised, and presentable at all times</li><li>Handle administrative tasks such as filing, data entry, and document preparation</li><li>Support the team with daily office coordination and operational needs</li></ul><p><strong>Who We’re Looking For</strong></p><ul><li>Excellent communication and customer service skills</li><li>Highly organised, detail-oriented, and able to multitask smoothly</li><li>Proficient with Google Workspace and Microsoft Office</li><li>Friendly, approachable, and professional in appearance and demeanour</li><li>Prior reception or admin experience is a plus — but not required</li></ul><p><strong>Why Join Us</strong></p><ul><li>Supportive and collaborative team culture</li><li>Opportunities to learn, grow, and develop new skills</li><li>Modern, comfortable, and welcoming workspace</li><li>Competitive remuneration and staff benefits</li><li>A company that genuinely values work–life balance</li></ul><p>If you enjoy meeting people, staying organised, and making an office run like clockwork, we’d love to hear from you.</p>",
